author: neels
msg: Cosmetic: Rename three local vars REPORT_BATON to REPORTER_BATON.
This baton goes with REPORTER and is usually implemented as a struct
reporter_baton_t. It actually wraps another baton; the wrapped baton
is called REPORT_BATON, goes with a REPORT and is usually implemented
as a report_baton_t. Be less confusing and match REPORTER to
